üëá Here's what you need to do ‚Äî in 4 steps:
STEP 1: Set up your chatbot backend (to talk to OpenAI)
Framer can‚Äôt talk directly to OpenAI (because of secret keys).
So, you need a little ‚Äúhelper‚Äù in between = called a serverless function.

We‚Äôll use Vercel (it‚Äôs free).

‚úÖ Go to: https://vercel.com
Login with GitHub

Create a new project

Choose ‚ÄúCreate from Template‚Äù > ‚ÄúOther‚Äù

